Returns a slice which contains items not yet handled by split.
# Example

```
#![feature(split_as_slice)]
let slice = [1,2,3,4,5];
let mut split = slice.split(|v| v % 2 == 0);
assert!(split.next().is_some());
assert_eq!(split.as_slice(), &[3,4,5]);
```
